track_notes: Free parking at the junction of the B6255 and B6479. This is a circular route. It is 4.2 miles to the summit and then 3.7m back, returning to Ribblehead using the steeper path down to Bruntscar.
track_title: G/NP-004 Whernside from Ribblehead circular route

track_notes: Parking spot on the road verge. Through gate and follow the wall up. Track kinks right then gets rough and steep to summit plateau. Capped trig point at summit.
